{"tid":2061061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「學術討論」香港人應學習《義勇軍進行曲》","createTime":"2020-06-12T06:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T13:34:26.000Z","uid":186,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c268a436dd849190d24ff67a83de484bd46eb0","tid":2061061,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:14:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你哋班連登仔好心學下唱《義勇軍進行曲》</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起來！不願做奴隸的人們！（起身啦！唔想做港奴的人們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n把我們的血肉，築成我們新的長城！（我地要不惜血肉，要建立<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新嘅</span></strong></span>長城）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中華民族到了最危險的時候，（中華民族依家到咗最危險嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每個人被迫着發出最後的吼聲。（咁慘烈 去到最後 迫住叫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n起來！起來！起來！（起身啦）<br />\n<br />\n我們萬眾一心，（我哋萬眾一心，一個共同目標）<br />\n<br />\n冒着敵人的炮火，前進！（敵人有炮火都要前進啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n冒着敵人的炮火，前進！（繼續向前）<br />\n<br />\n前進！前進！進！（一定要向前進，唔好退，唔好走）"},{"pid":"69bea6ec8fcba1d274b7cf6ea78837699751856c","tid":2061061,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:14:32.000Z","msg":"唔可以改歌詞"},{"pid":"0f4befba6e4ab87e4b39faff7ad5a3784dddb280","tid":2061061,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:15:00.000Z","msg":"每一句都係意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8082d2b3af865cdbd15ebbce6953ff731527bef9","tid":2061061,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:15:53.000Z","msg":"理解義勇軍進行曲"},{"pid":"dcc2659f3af3e6ecaa9ddb36acdedd90fdc00149","tid":2061061,"uid":14918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:17:31.000Z","msg":"先佔話語高地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準確理解義勇軍進行曲<br />\n堅決反抗極權政府入侵"},{"pid":"1ef2c41ba68bec2d850b9a04f2aa0d30b723dc50","tid":2061061,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"義勇軍進行曲 一定要唱<br />\n和你唱"},{"pid":"9da22a6983ee13760755547daa9e341f0ec0db61","tid":2061061,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />義士勇武"},{"pid":"afee4397ccbd67401d7ede969647ae84035e7b45","tid":2061061,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dcc2659f3af3e6ecaa9ddb36acdedd90fdc00149","tid":2061061,"uid":14918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:17:31.000Z","msg":"先佔話語高地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準確理解義勇軍進行曲<br />\n堅決反抗極權政府入侵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:20:41.000Z","msg":"義士勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184401436ad615992d2ab66ec13f7845916713c5","tid":2061061,"uid":189157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:20:56.000Z","msg":"唱完榮光再唱呢首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj